Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:05.65,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,This is for pushing me off my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:11.03,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,This is for leaving me unable to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:19.58,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,And this is for being born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:25.92,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sylvia-sama! Please, please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.16,0:00:27.75,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,This is cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:29.24,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:35.67,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,This Norma... this disgusting, \Nviolent, antisocial monster
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.67,0:00:37.80,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,was my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:41.18,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,What could be any worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:42.95,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:46.23,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Say you're sorry for being a Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:48.42,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sylvia-sama is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:51.44,Ange-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Give us back our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:55.39,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you, Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:59.49,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,You've given us this\N opportunity to dispense justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:05.25,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,It was I who exposed Angelise's \Nidentity at the Baptism Ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:13.69,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,After sixteen years, we finally \Nrid the royal family of this pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:16.93,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,All that remained was to wait, and hear that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:20.10,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd been sent to hell and \Ndevoured by another monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:21.72,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.16,0:01:25.89,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Much to my surprise, she did not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.50,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,She might have continued to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:34.55,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, Momoka, I sent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:37.15,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:40.79,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think a mere maid would simply
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:42.84,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,be allowed to meet with a Norma
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:45.33,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,banished to the ends of the earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.98,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,To see you fighting for Sylvia,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:52.02,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,not even knowing you were being manipulated...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:54.76,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was hilarious indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:56.32,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:57.84,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:02.90,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,The Empress died in her foolish \Nattempt to protect a Norma,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:06.62,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and the witless Emperor was \Nexecuted for deceiving the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.27,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Executed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:16.10,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Abominable Norma, Angelise,\N who carries the royal bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:20.53,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,With your judgment, the cleansing\N of the royal family will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:24.00,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, this nation will be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:26.79,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,The New Empire of Misurugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:30.55,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,As Julio the First, Emperor of the Holy Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.17,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I demand that this Norma be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:13.43,Ange-EpTitle,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(508,511)}Goodbye from the Gallows
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:17.90,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.98,Ange-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for lying to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:22.07,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:25.29,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I need to be executed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:27.07,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,For what crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.82,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:31.25,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember what you did to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:34.01,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I just kicked you around \Na little and tied you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:35.12,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:36.84,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,A little?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.23,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.21,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.38,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't warrant an execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.87,Ange-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,That's if you were a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:46.09,Ange-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Norma. You're not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:49.56,Ange-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,You made a lot of people \Nuncomfortable and unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.93,Ange-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,So you're being executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.38,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to die quietly over that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:54.52,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Like a farm animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.30,Ange-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Normas' fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.39,Ange-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.61,Ange-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Julio-sama says you get the death penalty,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.78,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so what's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.37,Ange-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.45,Ange-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Kill the Norma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.25,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's not her fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:09.20,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Angelise-sama didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:12.35,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,I found happiness thanks to Angelise-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.82,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hang her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.25,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hang her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:18.40,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hang her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.29,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hang her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.73,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hang her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.77,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hang her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:25.48,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:30.26,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Angelise-sama need to endure this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:31.92,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.18,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.85,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,And those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:38.77,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the only ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:42.07,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,...who accepted me without prejudice,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.49,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Norma or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.03,Ange-internal/narrator,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.52,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:56.53,Ange-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:58.84,Ange-top,C,0000,0000,0000,,Get it on video for me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:02.96,Ange-internal/narrator,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,These are the just, peace-loving \Npeople of Misurugi Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:06.13,Ange-internal/narrator,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,They're pigs. All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:10.26,Ange-internal/narrator,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,They're all unreasonable, ugly, stupid pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:14.81,Ange-internal/narrator,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we Norma have to go \Nthrough so much to keep them alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.77,Ange-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Angelise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.65,Ange-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:24.51,Ange-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,May the light protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.07,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.86,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.99,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.12,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:35.42,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,The light of the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:40.14,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,Sparkle, sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.14,Ange-main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:41.56,Ange-main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:45.22,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,The light of the end
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:43.99,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.88,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,The Endless Song.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.09,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mother's song.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.11,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ruin it, you Norma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:53.53,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.56,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,Guards, make her stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:53.26,Ange-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:57.30,Ange-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:07:03.18,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,The time flows from the hour glass
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.46,Ange-internal/narrator,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,This guiding light...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.94,Ange-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all that Mother left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.01,Ange-internal/narrator,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:16.08,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,The many millions of lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:11.11,Ange-internal/narrator,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.74,Ange-internal/narrator,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Try to kill me if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.46,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:21.76,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.55,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,This is goodbye, Angelise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:32.38,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angelise-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:53.36,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:56.83,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:58.91,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.79,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,Guards, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.50,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and restrain them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:08.35,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,That Norma-saver. What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:09.63,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,A rebel element.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.85,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,A Norma-sympathizing terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:15.18,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Angelise-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.14,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.28,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Release.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:26.01,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them if you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.20,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:35.86,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.87,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, use these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.28,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like a Para-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:50.63,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Get on, Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:51.55,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,We're escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.05,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:53.80,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:58.97,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Angelise, why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.64,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Onii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:04.20,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You revealed my true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.87,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sylvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:10.52,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You showed me the true, \Nfilthy nature of human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:15.11,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, beasts from a rotten nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:19.91,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,After her! After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:28.08,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.41,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.35,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Angelise-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.70,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.67,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I feel refreshed, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:47.48,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:54.21,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I realized I don't have \Nfamily or friends or a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:56.52,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Angelise-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:58.36,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:00.87,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.12,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:06.47,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good. Ange, you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.42,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:09.86,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:11.97,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:15.55,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep burying \Nyour face in my crotch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:18.30,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a habit? A tic? A sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.18,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.01,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:26.56,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Angelise-sama, what is your \Nrelationship with this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:28.76,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:31.64,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,A special relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:32.31,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:38.01,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Otherwise, he wouldn't \Nrisk his life to come help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:42.32,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Spring has come, even for \Nmy tomboyish Angelise-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:45.91,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,As your top maid, there's nothing \Nthat could make me happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.74,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:49.79,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.00,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.32,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I got a message from Jill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.81,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Jill?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:10:59.00,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:01.78,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,She said not to let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.01,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.53,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.54,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:14.19,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:18.24,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Knight of Villkiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.25,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.28,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,A knight to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:23.82,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,You can ask Jill for the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:26.48,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:29.18,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:34.34,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair's a beautiful blonde color.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.25,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,S-So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:38.86,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You're blonde down there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.97,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Die, pervert knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:53.44,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:54.85,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.05,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:01.06,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:03.56,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:04.16,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:07.45,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I would have been dead if not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.50,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I was trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:13.97,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never heard such a \Nbeautiful, enchanting voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:15.13,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,It was a nice song.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:22.23,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never heard it before, yet it \Nwas somehow nostalgic and happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.19,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,A strange song.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:26.47,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:27.81,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:34.27,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving Angelise-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.83,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite a lucky fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:42.53,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting a man to give you a ride home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.73,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Jill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:47.57,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:48.98,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:50.12,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:53.75,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Only after you're done reflecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.51,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Angelise-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.35,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Ange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.68,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:15.54,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.27,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.19,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.50,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.82,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:30.75,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.50,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You're being informed of your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.86,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Ange of Salia Squad, for your desertion,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.96,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you will be placed in the \Nsuspension quarters for one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:43.07,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Your wealth and property \Nwill all be confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.32,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,This includes the Villkiss, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:49.01,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,You have to take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.66,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,You're a deserter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.28,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.56,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.50,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:57.52,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.84,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,We've been here since we were babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:04.99,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know the outside world, \Nand there's no one waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.18,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a reason to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:10.60,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place for us Norma to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.03,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:15.70,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, it's because \Nshe's different from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.28,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have trusted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.24,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:38.40,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:41.86,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Hilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:44.89,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.88,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You're back, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.12,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.01,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I said stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.75,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.47,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,What did they do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:05.46,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,You ought to talk first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.54,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:14.64,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I was stripped down, whipped, \Nmocked, and hanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:17.85,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.03,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Hilda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:23.22,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I was beaten by fifty men.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.27,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:27.36,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I took 'em all down, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:31.32,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you took quite a beating, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:33.78,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.95,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Did you meet your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.91,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:43.28,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.72,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:00.81,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.25,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.42,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:11.90,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,How strange. Are you depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:12.99,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.75,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.41,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:22.04,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of all people, Mom would accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:23.27,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:27.79,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Mom would\N forgive me for being a Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:31.34,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,But she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:35.02,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be a Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:40.02,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere outside for a Norma to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:44.10,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You have your friends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.56,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.06,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:53.13,Ange-flashback,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,Hilda's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:57.12,Ange-flashback,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why did you desert us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:00.49,Ange-flashback,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't you talk to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.84,Ange-flashback,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.54,Ange-flashback,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,She never thought of us as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.34,Ange-flashback,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,You finally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:12.57,Ange-flashback,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought of you \Nas friends to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:17.30,Ange-flashback,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I was just playing along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.25,Ange-flashback,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:21.65,Ange-flashback,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.98,Ange-flashback,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,You should have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:31.12,Ange-flashback,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,C-Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.57,Ange-flashback,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Rosalie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:33.65,Ange-flashback,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:37.25,Ange-flashback,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,I bought back all of Captain Zola's stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.74,Ange-flashback,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.54,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:54.83,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,My room, my money, my reason to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:56.18,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:58.30,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they'd just kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.18,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.97,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:04.52,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:10.47,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you were royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:12.11,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,You talk different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:14.64,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a piece of shit at rock bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:16.29,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,And you still tell me to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.94,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Not to give up hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.24,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.95,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You'll stink if you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.20,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.15,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,So don't. Not in this tiny space.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:28.30,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.53,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.46,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,How selfish are you, you bitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.01,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk, loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.22,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.59,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Do you honestly believe such a thing exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:48.11,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,All that exists is persecution\N and fighting DRAGONs every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:52.31,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. It's almost funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:55.98,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Those ignorant bastards are brimming\N with prejudice and bigotry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.92,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,They hear I'm a Norma,\N and they reject me like idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.37,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Is it {\i1}that{\i0} bad that I can't use Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.79,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Is it bad that I'm different?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.75,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:14.53,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship, family, social bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:20.53,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I said friendship is \Ngreat and bonds are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.76,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I want to beat myself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:25.68,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:28.18,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:30.95,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbasses everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.90,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,The world's rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.36,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,How about we destroy it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.54,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:39.93,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:42.57,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,With our Para-mails and Arzenal's weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:45.41,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,How far do you think it is to the continent?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.62,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,We'll run out of fuel, and then it's {\i1}splash{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:51.03,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to build something\N that can make the trip, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:52.63,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,What about food?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:54.72,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty of fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.28,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Or we could steal from \Nthe humans, if we had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:58.78,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,And materials?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.14,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,We'd figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:07.67,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,This world oppressed me, \Nhumiliated me and degraded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:09.85,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reject it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:15.77,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,This wretched, frustrating, \Ninfuriating world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:17.70,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,It's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:18.36,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:22.99,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying it's bullshit. All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:28.53,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's destroy this bullshit world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:29.70,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,The whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:31.58,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.63,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.42,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I want to destroy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.89,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine upon me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:49.43,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon everything
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.48,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,It spins and spins
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:56.27,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:21:00.88,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness and happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:04.40,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:06.11,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,Quiz time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:09.00,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,Who's singing this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:11.04,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:10.37,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Ange-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.54,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:16.00,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:15.54,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:20.25,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:18.58,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Salia-chan's going to get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:20.47,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Ange is a deserter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:24.51,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.97,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,How could you be won over by a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.51,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,That's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:27.34,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:31.77,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Ange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.76,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:37.56,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,Resonate now as your true form
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.90,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleetingly, fleetingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:39.90,Ange-main,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:45.24,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,Above the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:44.69,Ange-main,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,Rosalie, you... you wouldn't abandon me, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:50.66,Ange-internaltop,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:29.05,next episode preview,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,519)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:29.41,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like we're finally friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:31.73,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,That was predictable. I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.73,0:23:33.35,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,No one's died in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:35.06,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Normally someone dies when they become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:36.05,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I bet next week—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.05,0:23:38.37,Ange-top,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your friend, dummy.
